column1:
The striking resemblance continues—it's like
we're back in the depths of Mementos, staring
down the Holy Grail...

Welcome. You have reached your ultimate
destination.

This is the Promised Land, the paradise for all
humanity.

A place for the masses to find salvation.
The answer to every Desire.

Is that voice... coming from the box?
Just who are you!?

I am EMMA, the Ark of the Covenant and
guide for all mankind.

Hey, someone tell me what's going on!
What the hell IS that thing!?
Me too. Explain this in comprehensible terms.
We don't get any of this either!

My primary directive is to grant humanity
its ultimate Desire...
To be liberated from all pain and suffering.

Mankind cannot bring themselves to
implement the solution, and instead
beg for deliverance.

I shall become a god to grant them this
deliverance. I shall guide them to the
Promised Land.
